QuestData.Title: Legendary Heroes
QuestData.CompletionText: Your radiate command and power, $C. Exalted in the eyes of Frostwolf - the enemy cowers at the mention of your name.$B$BRise, Hero of Frostwolf. Rise and be honored!$B$BPresent your insignia.
QuestData.RewardText: Soon, all on the field of battle will be under your watchful eye. Command of the Valley and its troops will be yours!
